videos.headline: Memphis scores first with 45-yard TD pass
videos.description: Riley Ferguson throws to Troy Pollard, who weaves his way through the Western Kentucky defense for a 45-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Western Kentucky gets on the board with short TD strike
videos.description: Down 7-0, Mike White throws a four-yard touchdown pass to Stevie Donatelli to tie Western Kentucky's game with Memphis at seven.

videos.headline: Lineman scores TD for Western Kentucky in Boca Raton Bowl
videos.description: Western Kentucky lineman Forrest Lamp gets the ball and goes in for the nine-yard touchdown to give the Hilltoppers the lead.

videos.headline: Western Kentucky's Joel Iyiegbuniwe ejected for Targeting
videos.description: Ferguson, Riley pass incomplete to Pollard, Tony, PENALTY WESTERNKY personal foul 15 yards to the MEMPHIS45, NO PLAY, 1ST DOWN MEMPHIS.

videos.headline: Western Kentucky's Iyiegbuniwe ejected for targeting
videos.description: Tony Pollard tries to catch the catch, but he is hit hard by Western Kentucky's Joel Iyiegbuniwe, who would be ejected from the game for targeting.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Western Kentucky's Iyiegbuniwe ejected for targeting) 2016/12/20

videos.headline: Western Kentucky pads bowl lead with 37-yard TD pass
videos.description: Mike White throws his second touchdown pass of the game with a 37-yard strike to Nicholas Norris, giving Western Kentucky a 21-10 lead over Memphis.

videos.headline: R. Ferguson pass to A. Miller for 7 yds for a TD
videos.description: Riley Ferguson pass complete to Anthony Miller for 7 yds for a TD

videos.headline: Wales punches in short TD to keep Western Kentucky in front
videos.description: Anthony Wales gets the handoff and runs in for the two-yard touchdown to give Western Kentucky a 28-17 lead over Memphis.

videos.headline: Memphis denies Western Kentucky a TD with INT in end zone
videos.description: Mike White throws deep and finds Taywan Taylor in the end zone, but Dontrell Nelson wrestles it away from Taylor for a Memphis interception.

videos.headline: Western Kentucky goes up big with 41-yard TD pass to Taylor
videos.description: Western Kentucky comes out firing in the second half when Mike White throws deep and finds Taywan Taylor for a 41-yard touchdown to give the Hilltoppers a 35-17 lead over Memphis.

videos.headline: Memphis turns the ball over on a fumble
videos.description: Riley Ferguson run for a loss of 5 yards to the Memph 21 Riley Ferguson fumbled, recovered by WKent Nick Dawson-Brents

videos.headline: Wales picks up another rushing TD for Western Kentucky
videos.description: Antony Wales rushes in for a three-yard touchdown to give Western Kentucky a 41-17 lead over Memphis in the Boca Raton Bowl.

videos.headline: R. Ferguson pass to A. Miller for 10 yds for a TD
videos.description: Riley Ferguson pass complete to Anthony Miller for 10 yds for a TD

videos.headline: Western Kentucky gets big gain on flea flicker
videos.description: Mike White pass complete to Taywan Taylor for 38 yds to the Memph 37 for a 1ST down

videos.headline: R. Ferguson pass intercepted, K. Brown return for 8 yds
videos.description: Riley Ferguson pass intercepted Keith Brown return for 8 yds to the Memph 30

videos.headline: Memphis scores a 45 yard TD to convert on 4th down
videos.description: Riley Ferguson pass complete to Anthony Miller for 45 yds for a TD

videos.headline: Wales seals the deal for Western Kentucky with another TD
videos.description: Anthony Wales runs in for his third touchdown of the game to give Western Kentucky a 51-31 lead over Memphis.

videos.headline: Western Kentucky tops Memphis to win Boca Raton Bowl
videos.description: Anthony Wales rushes for 245 yards and three touchdowns as Western Kentucky wins the Boca Raton Bowl with a 51-31 victory over Memphis.
